    "ShortDescription": "Brown, Orange, Green, Pink & Purple Line trains are running with delays from congestion due to signal problems. Crews working to restore normal service.",
    "FullDescription": {
      "#cdata-section": "<p>Brown, Orange, Green, Pink &amp; Purple Line trains are running with delays from congestion resulting from earlier signal problems near Adams/Wabash.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Crews are working to clear the congestion that&#39;s formed and restore normal travel times through the area.&nbsp;Trains and platforms may be busier than usual at this time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some Loop-bound trains may also be turned back toward their terminal to help alleviate congestion more quickly. Listen for any announcements on board your train.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Allow extra travel time.</p>\r\n"
